Class ModbusBlockImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus.impl.ModbusBlockImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModbusBlock

    public class ModbusBlockImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements ModbusBlock
    An implementation of the model object 'Block'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Id
    • Block Type
    • Start Address
    • Count
    • Period
    • Timeout
    • Type
